author: Jonathan Swan
title: Some aides eye May 1 start to coronavirus reopening
description: President Trump's aides, encouraged by virus data showing fewer deaths than once projected, are working behind the scenes to deliver on his vow to reopen America "sooner rather than later." What to watch for: The official said there’s a lot of internal energy…
